<h2>What is SAP?</h2>

<p>
SAP is one of the world's leading enterprise software companies.
It develops software that helps organizations manage business
operations, finance, supply chains, human resources,
and customer relationships.
</p>

<p>
Founded in Germany in 1972, SAP created some of the most widely
used enterprise resource planning (ERP) systems in the world.
These platforms integrate data across departments and help
companies run their operations more efficiently.
</p>

<p>
Today, SAP technologies are used by thousands of organizations
across industries such as manufacturing, logistics, finance,
energy, and retail.
</p>

<p>
Iransap.com is an independent initiative focused on sharing
knowledge and raising awareness about enterprise technologies
within the Iranian technology community.
</p>

